- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper focuses on human characteristics and behaviors that make them vulnerable to Malware attacks.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is relevant as the paper discusses the financial losses experienced by organizations and users due to Malware attacks.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also relevant as the paper discusses the exploitation of human trust and curiosity by Malware.
